#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.20"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.20:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.20:0.2"
msgid "2. Caravagga"
msgstr "2. Walking"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: bhattuddesasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.20:0.3"
msgid "20. Bhattuddesakasutta"
msgstr "20. A Meal-allocator"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.20:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Catūhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhattuddesako yathābhataṃ nikkhitto "
"evaṃ niraye."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a meal-allocator who has four qualities is cast down to hell."

msgctxt "an4.20:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.20:1.3"
msgid ""
"Chandāgatiṃ gacchati, dosāgatiṃ gacchati, mohāgatiṃ gacchati, bhayāgatiṃ "
"gacchati—"
msgstr ""
"They make decisions prejudiced by favoritism, hostility, stupidity, and "
"cowardice."

msgctxt "an4.20:1.4"
msgid ""
"imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato bhattuddesako yathābhataṃ "
"nikkhitto evaṃ niraye."
msgstr "A meal-allocator who has these four qualities is cast down to hell."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.20:2.1"
msgid ""
"Catūhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhattuddesako yathābhataṃ nikkhitto "
"evaṃ sagge."
msgstr "A meal-allocator who has four qualities is raised up to heaven."

msgctxt "an4.20:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.20:2.3"
msgid ""
"Na chandāgatiṃ gacchati, na dosāgatiṃ gacchati, na mohāgatiṃ gacchati, na "
"bhayāgatiṃ gacchati—"
msgstr ""
"They make decisions unprejudiced by favoritism, hostility, stupidity, and "
"cowardice."

msgctxt "an4.20:2.4"
msgid ""
"imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato bhattuddesako yathābhataṃ "
"nikkhitto evaṃ saggeti."
msgstr "A meal-allocator who has these four qualities is raised up to heaven."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.20:3.1"
msgid "Ye keci kāmesu asaññatā janā,"
msgstr "All those people with uncontrolled sensuality,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.20:3.2"
msgid "Adhammikā honti adhammagāravā;"
msgstr "unprincipled, with no respect for principle,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: Chandā dosā mohā ca bhayā gāmino → chandā ca dosā ca bhayā ca gāmino (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.20:3.3"
msgid "Chandā dosā mohā ca bhayā gāmino,"
msgstr "led astray by favoritism, hatred, stupidity, or cowardice,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: Parisākasaṭo → parisakkasāvo (bj, pts1) | parisakasaṭo (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an4.20:3.4"
msgid "Parisākasaṭo ca panesa vuccati."
msgstr "are called ‘an assembly of the dregs’:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.20:4.1"
msgid "Evañhi vuttaṃ samaṇena jānatā,"
msgstr "that’s what was said by the ascetic who knows."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.20:4.2"
msgid "Tasmā hi te sappurisā pasaṃsiyā;"
msgstr "And so those good, praiseworthy people,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.20:4.3"
msgid "Dhamme ṭhitā ye na karonti pāpakaṃ,"
msgstr "standing on principle, doing nothing wrong,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: na dosā na mohā na bhayā ca gāmino → na chandadosā na bhayā ca gāmino (bj, s1-3, km) | na chandā dosā na bhayā ca gāmino (pts1)
msgctxt "an4.20:4.4"
msgid "Na chandā na dosā na mohā na bhayā ca gāmino;"
msgstr "not led astray by favoritism, hatred, stupidity, or cowardice,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.20:4.5"
msgid "Parisāya maṇḍo ca panesa vuccati,"
msgstr "are called ‘an assembly of the cream’:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.20:4.6"
msgid "Evañhi vuttaṃ samaṇena jānatā”ti."
msgstr "that’s what was said by the ascetic who knows.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.20:4.7"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.20:4.8"
msgid "Caravaggo dutiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.20:5.1"
msgid "Caraṃ sīlaṃ padhānāni,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.20:5.2"
msgid "saṃvaraṃ paññatti pañcamaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.20:5.3"
msgid "Sokhummaṃ tayo agatī,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.20:5.4"
msgid "bhattuddesena te dasāti."
msgstr ""
